<section id="content">

<blockquote>
	<q>I&#39;ve never known a musician who regretted being one. Whatever deceptions life may have in store for you, music itself is not going to let you down.</q>
	<cite><a href="/author/202">Virgil Thompson</a></cite>
	<footer>contributed by <a href="/contributor/60">Julia&Tarik Banzi</a></footer>
</blockquote>

